text: Beautiful NTUC FairPrice that boosts a variety of essential items and food. There is a fresh seafood area, with poultry meats and even sushi which is hard to find in neighborhood Ntucs! You can definitely find more exotic items and the place is quite huge. The supermarket will definitely help the residents nearby. When checking out, the staff was really kind and friendly. Nice cozy FairPrice.

Excited to have a new Fairprice in Senja, with ample space between rows and a good selection of produce. Bonuses include live stations for sushi, yakitori, roast meats, and even a mini polar cake & puff stand. If they add a bakery section with fresh loaves, it will be perfect.
The Cashier this morning was efficient and provide excellent service with a smile, although the queue was long, Ms Koh, efficiently cleared it in no time. Thumb up for the service.

Friendly staff at the cashier.

Wide ranges of products on top of the usual groceries. It also has sushi, roast meats (chicken, duck, pork etc), ready-to-eat meal (e.g. yakitori rice), polar puff corner, steamed buns, etc.
This supermarket specialises are Polar Puff pastries already sold out around 5pm+. There's a sushi corner, BBQ corner, Japanese Bento and steamed bao.
